plot: The Roaring 20's a time of prosperity. Jazz is king, the Mob rules the streets, and Demons are running a mock. Enter Sister Rosette Christopher, of the Order of Magdaline, an elite group out to destroy the evil. Along with her faithful companion and contractor Chrono, a devil, they go on wild gun slinging adventures. But Rosette's ultimate quest is to find her little brother Joshua, who was kidnapped by Lord Aion. Can Rosette save her brother?   Written by  arorashadow_2003
title: Chrono Crusade
